{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.600", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.880", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.040", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ministerin Hendricks hat meine Worte vorweggenommen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.160", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum es heute am wenigsten gehen sollte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.560", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist die Zukunft des Dieselmotors. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.800", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum es heute eigentlich gehen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.240", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist der Schutz der Gesundheit der Bev\u00f6lkerung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.440", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht um die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wer die Verantwortung daf\u00fcr tr\u00e4gt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.840", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die europ\u00e4ischen Grenzwerte f\u00fcr Stickoxide acht Jahre nach Beginn ihrer G\u00fcltigkeit immer noch nicht eingehalten werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und es geht um die Frage, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.360", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was man mit dieser im wahrsten Sinne des Wortes v\u00f6llig verfahrenen Lage anf\u00e4ngt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.320", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundesregierung wusste schon fr\u00fch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.920", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass hier offensichtlich ein ganzer Industriezweig die Einstellung entwickelt hat: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.000", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnen tun und lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.520", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was wir wollen.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Umgang der Autoindustrie mit Gesetzen und damit letztlich auch mit dem Leben und der Gesundheit von Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "scheint so zu sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.720", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man Gesetze als Vorschl\u00e4ge ansieht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Vorschl\u00e4ge ver\u00e4ndert man so lange, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.120", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bis sie einem passen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.880", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und was macht die Bundesregierung? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt die Autoindustrie endlich zu effektiven Ma\u00dfnahmen zu zwingen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.600", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "l\u00e4sst sie sich auf lasche Vereinbarungen mit diesen Gesetzesbrechern ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.800", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es wird, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.640", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn \u00fcberhaupt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.240", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "lediglich die Software ver\u00e4ndert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.120", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und die Regierung verzichtet auf f\u00e4llige Strafzahlungen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.680", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was f\u00fcr ein schmutziger Deal!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.920", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ein schmutziger Deal auf Kosten derer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.560", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die unter Atemwegserkrankungen leiden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.360", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein schmutziger Deal zulasten der Gesundheit aller, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.800", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch wenn das heute kleingeredet worden ist."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.120", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Politik und Wirtschaft in einem so unglaublichen Ma\u00dfe versagen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.760", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann muss sich wohl eine Umweltorganisation auf den Weg durch die juristischen Instanzen machen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.560", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um dem Recht zum Durchbruch zu verhelfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.520", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich m\u00f6chte an dieser Stelle die Gelegenheit nutzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.880", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Deutschen Umwelthilfe f\u00fcr ihr langj\u00e4hriges, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.520", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hartn\u00e4ckiges und letztendlich erfolgreiches Engagement im Bereich der Luftreinheit zu danken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.920", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der wichtigste Teil der kurzfristigen L\u00f6sung ist also klar: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.800", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Autoindustrie muss die Fahrzeuge auf eigene Kosten mit einer funktionierenden Abgasreinigung ausstatten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "141.920", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie k\u00f6nnen die betrogenen K\u00e4ufer mit diesem Problem nicht alleinlassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "141.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.680", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die haben sich auf die Versprechen der Autoindustrie verlassen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.320", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann muss die Autoindustrie auch liefern."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.440", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "An dieser Stelle noch ein Wort zur AfD. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "157.240", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie haben ein vormodernes Verst\u00e4ndnis von Demokratie und Industriepolitik."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "157.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.720", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie meinen offenbar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.640", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit \u201eGrenzwerte rauf!\u201c und \u201eRaus aus der EU!\u201c w\u00fcrden alle Probleme verschwinden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie mit all Ihren Politikans\u00e4tzen werden Sie auch damit den Problemen unserer Gesellschaft nicht gerecht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.880", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und Sie wollen ja auch gar keine Probleme l\u00f6sen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.280", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen provozieren und sonst nichts."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Worum es heute also wirklich gehen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.200", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.720", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sind die Herausforderungen f\u00fcr die Mobilit\u00e4t im 21.\u00a0Jahrhundert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.840", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zu diesen Herausforderungen geh\u00f6rt das Thema Luftreinheit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.240", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dazu geh\u00f6rt aber auch der Klimawandel insgesamt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.320", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dazu geh\u00f6rt notwendige und bezahlbare Mobilit\u00e4t f\u00fcr alle Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.400", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und dazu geh\u00f6rt der \u00fcberf\u00e4llige Umbau unserer St\u00e4dte in lebenswerte St\u00e4dte."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Regierung hat im Feld der Luftreinheit in den letzten Jahren komplett versagt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.680", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber eine Idee war gut: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.560", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre Idee eines kostenlosen \u00d6PNV."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.760", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist wirklich eine brillante Idee. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke ermutigen Sie ausdr\u00fccklich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich weiterhin ernsthaft mit dieser Idee zu besch\u00e4ftigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.520", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das geht allerdings nur, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.920", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn wir sicherstellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.800", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass in einem neuen Nahverkehrs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.000", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "oder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.320", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "besser, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.360", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mobilit\u00e4tsplan alle Verkehrstr\u00e4ger ber\u00fccksichtigt werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.880", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir diesen Weg gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "232.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.960", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann m\u00fcssen wir auch die langfristige Finanzierung des kostenlosen \u00d6PNV gew\u00e4hrleisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen also einen umfassenden Plan f\u00fcr eine soziale und \u00f6kologische Verkehrswende. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "249.440", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu muss auch der Umstieg auf das Rad und die eigenen F\u00fc\u00dfe attraktiver gestaltet werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "249.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.160", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das bedeutet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "254.680", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen viel mehr Platz f\u00fcr Radfahrer und Fu\u00dfg\u00e4nger und f\u00fcr moderne\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "254.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.280", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sprich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sozial-\u00f6kologische\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Massenbef\u00f6rderungsmittel;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.880", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben ja eben schon einige Beispiele geh\u00f6rt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "267.560", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann sparen wir 100\u00a0Prozent der Emissionen ein und schaffen St\u00e4dte mit hoher Lebensqualit\u00e4t."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "267.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "272.240", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt da dieses sch\u00f6ne Zitat des ehemaligen B\u00fcrgermeisters von Bogot\u00e1, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "272.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "273.800", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Enrique Pe\u00f1alosa. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "273.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "275.280", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er sagte:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "275.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.440", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ob eine Stadt zivilisiert ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "280.200", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "h\u00e4ngt nicht von der Zahl ihrer Schnellstra\u00dfen ab, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "280.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "281.040", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern davon, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
